reviews.text:
I like the environment here: wooden table / chairs etc. But the foods and service can be improved. Not up to Japanese standard. 

The sandwiches with egg... too much tomato 🍅 and the toast too thick etc.
Not so oily and balance of mountain and sea origin food.

Huge store with a wide range of products, not limited to snacks, cloth, but also books, magazine, and cafe.
Products with high quality as usual, and this Muji store is spacious.  Design just same as other stores, which is clean and simple, and this store is very clean as well.
But now staffs here are limited, not easy to find a help when needed

This Japanese life-style store provides a very pleasant shopping experience.
It offers apparel, beauty products, travel accessories and packaged food/snacks. There is a wide variety of household goods to choose from; such as furniture, small appliances, kitchen/table-ware, plastic storage units and magazine/file holders
In addition, there is a book and a stationery section. There is even a Muji Cafe inside the store for good measure.
Superb customer service. The staff is polite and always eager to help.
This is a larger Muji store with a cafe and a books section.

reviews.text:
Muji Cafe never fails me. They've a good variety of food with high quality and the people are nice and always ready to offer good services.
The wood furniture is making it a lot better!
每人平均一百元的價錢，享受大學飯堂格局的食品，只是食材及環境較好。
坐得幾舒服，食物普通一般水準，選擇配搭多。蛋糕質地細緻，咖啡十份普通。侍應十分有禮，配合文清feel。

Can never go wrong with muji cafe, it's a healthy, filling and reasonably priced option, that I'll never grow tired of.
The food are very seasonal and options are plenty. Would recommend to everyone I know.
聽好吃的，略貴
